        </ab></refsDecl></encodingDesc><revisionDesc status="proposed"><change who="MAM" when="2019-06-12">Automatisch angelegt aus Buchausgabe</change><change who="GHS" when="2020-08-17">Durchsicht</change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><facsimile><graphic url="1909_AS_RBH_1_00034"/><graphic url="1909_AS_RBH_1_00035"/><graphic url="1909_AS_RBH_1_00036"/><graphic url="1909_AS_RBH_1_00037"/></facsimile><text type="letter"><body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00034"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb47570">Hotel <c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/> Pension Bavaria</rs><rs ref="#pmb11483" type="place">Meran-Obermais</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print">Hotel <c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/> Pension <rs ref="#pmb723" type="place">Wildbad Warmbrunn</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb724">Pustertal</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print">Besitzer: <rs ref="#pmb47572" type="person">Jos. Böhm</rs></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Dr. Richard</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb909">Velden</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb430">am Wörthersee</rs></addrLine><addrLine>am <rs ref="#pmb40118" type="place">Etab. Wahliss</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00035"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb47570">Hotel <c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/> Pension Bavaria</rs></hi></p><p><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb11483" type="place">Meran-Obermais</rs></hi></p><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print">Hotel <c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/> Pension</hi></p><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb723" type="place">Wildbad Warmbrunn</rs></hi></p><p rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb724">Pustertal</rs> (<rs ref="#pmb423" type="place">Tirol</rs>)</hi></p><opener><dateline rend="center"><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00036"/><rs ref="#pmb723" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Welsb.-Waldbr.</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1907-08-25">25. 8 907</date></dateline><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>wir fahren morgen <date>26.</date> von hier fort. (<rs ref="#pmb12692" type="person">Heini</rs> direct nach <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>.) <rs ref="#pmb2173" type="person">Olga</rs> u ich (höch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>twahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich) <rs ref="#pmb40343" type="place">Waidbruck</rs>, übernachten. Da<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> durchs <rs ref="#pmb40350" type="place">Grödner Thal</rs>, <rs ref="#pmb40346" type="place">Grödnerjoch</rs>, <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40366" type="place">Corvara</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40354" type="place">Arabba</rs></hi> – <rs ref="#pmb40369" type="place">Pordoj</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40362" type="place">Vigo</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40371" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Karer</hi><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs> – <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Bozen</hi></rs>. Manches zu Fu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s, manches zu Wagen; Modificationen nicht ausge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlo<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en. Höch<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>twahr<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheinlich Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag oder So<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>tag<tei:space unit="chars" quantity="1"></tei:space><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind wir in <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place">Bozen</rs>, wollen aber <add place="above">von</add> dort direct nach <rs ref="#pmb43520" type="place">Meran</rs> weiter, um dort, in <pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00037"/>dem uns lebhaft empfohlenen parkumgebenen <rs ref="#pmb41086" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Palasthotel</hi></rs> etwa 8 Tage zu bleiben. Da<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> wohl (vielleicht mit Aufenthalt in <rs ref="#pmb40260" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Bozen</hi></rs> (<rs ref="#pmb41083" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Mendel</hi></rs>) – <rs ref="#pmb867" type="place">I<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>sbruck</rs> (<anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL-1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41093" subtype="implied"><rs ref="#pmb5626" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Theoderich</hi></rs></rs><note type="commentary" xml:id="KL-1h">Die Statue <rs ref="#pmb5626" type="person">Theoderichs des Großen</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb41097" type="person">Peter Vischer</rs> (dem Älteren) in der <rs ref="#pmb41093" type="place">Innsbrucker Hofkirche</rs> spielt in <rs ref="#pmb2121" type="person">Schnitzler</rs>s Erzählung <rs ref="#pmb33776" type="work">Dämmerseele</rs> eine zentrale Rolle. </note>) – <rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs> (<rs ref="#pmb30" type="place">Salzburg</rs>)–) nach <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>. –</p><p>Ein Telegra<c rendition="#gemination-m"/><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><subst><del rend="strikethrough"><date>Freitag</date></del><add place="above"><date>Donnerstag</date></add></subst><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40371" type="place">Karersee</rs> post rest.</hi> hat Chance uns zu erreichen. Vielleicht ent<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chließen Sie<tei:space unit="chars" quantity="1"></tei:space><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich auch zu <rs ref="#pmb43520" type="place">Meran</rs>. <rs ref="#pmb39975" type="place">Gardasee</rs> werden wir diesmal (diesmal<c rendition="#dots" n="3"/>!) wohl nicht mitnehmen. In dem <rs ref="#pmb40371" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Karer</hi><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ee</rs>telegr. vermerken Sie vielleicht, we<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>s geht, wo Sie <date>Sam<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><pb facs="1907_AS_RBH_1_00037"/>u <date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n"/>tag</date> telegr. zu erreichen<tei:space unit="chars" quantity="1"></tei:space><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ind. –</p><p><rs ref="#pmb11485" type="person">Goldmann</rs> i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t mit <rs type="person" ref="#pmb17163" subtype="implied">Mutter</rs> in <rs ref="#pmb40474" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Gossensass</hi></rs> verblieben, wie er mir auf mündl. Weg ausrichten lie<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s. –</p><p>Leben Sie wohl,<tei:space unit="chars" quantity="1"></tei:space><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>eien Sie alle gegrüßt und la<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie mich hoffen, d<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s wir einander bald wieder<tei:space unit="chars" quantity="1"></tei:space><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen.</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div></body></text></TEI>